{"tid":1631644,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【突發】【重要】一齊為前線手足正名！","createTime":"2019-10-06T15:59:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T16:04:21.000Z","uid":305449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4393cbdcb5dd10b9130c9bc707eaea1672ed281f","tid":1631644,"uid":305449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:59:11.000Z","msg":"一齊嗌新名：<br />\n中文：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">保護香港市民隊(護民隊) </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>Civil Protection Force(CPF) </strong></span><br />\n<br />\n唔好再叫獅鳥，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">前線手足係人唔係神獸，呢個世界冇人係神</span>，係保護香港市民免受<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">中共暴徒</span>以及<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港魔警</span>既暴力傷害及制止恐怖襲擊，讓香港市民能擁有免於恐懼既自由！<br />\n<br />\n唔該咁多位圍觀既，唔好再嗌神獸，一齊嗌「保護市民」，「為民除害」，「港人自救」<br />\n<br />\n請支持<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">護民隊 CPF</span></strong>"},{"pid":"cecda2021e2205a0f539938ec67dce187ce2b951","tid":1631644,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:00:11.000Z","msg":"大家知唔知道宜家外國人點諗勇武<br />\n勇武要大家backup 啊！<br />\n記唔記得當初應承過<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>核彈都唔割</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n正式宣布：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">文宣洗地</span></strong></span>開始［行動po求置頂］<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630198\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630198</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d89073f12b9e40f6d63985c61b674e7504b4ca51","tid":1631644,"uid":75959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:02:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">大家 呢幾日都係行動日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但連登都無比大陸DDos攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就證明左係大量五毛做緊野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又分化又風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地係時候要醒下<br />\n<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰<br />\n<br />\n跟住就係開始做正經野：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 推紅色的士撞人單野<br />\n<br />\n2.推黑警又當街踢人單野<br />\n<br />\n3.九龍塘軍營入面有綠色防暴警既片<br />\n<br />\n4.解釋返裝修既原因比外國知<br />\n<br />\n5.宣傳黑紅藍黃既概念<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />光復香港，時代革命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地唔好再比五毛搞爆連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"e531e0a85388aa6526519949bc4f844a6adf1f7e","tid":1631644,"uid":305449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:03:29.000Z","msg":"雖然有d膠，但係勇武必須得到正名！<br />\n唔該搞大佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76324691202a3db7ecc422c27371eb0e4faf51f6","tid":1631644,"uid":305449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:04:21.000Z","msg":"幫手推<br />\n護民隊<br />\nCivil Protection Force! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}